20462,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>份工有需要咪去考 如果唔係考完真係無乜機會用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩工會有用<br />\n做開文職工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇乜機會用<br />\n<br />\n除非你公司有條好撚索既女突然暈底，而你又識急救，呢個時候你又可以名正言順咁將隻手放係佢個胸上面，又可以人工呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n如果你公司冇女就算啦"},{"pid":"f51650c87a77b3b3605e9e4265d4336dcb2f22f2","tid":220462,"uid":70622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:10:14.000Z","msg":"考左先實冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565777fd0c09f92c4ee2564275ead7099a2299d3","tid":220462,"uid":32549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份工有需要咪去考 如果唔係考完真係無乜機會用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩工會有用<br />\n做開文職工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇乜機會用<br />\n<br />\n除非你公司有條好撚索既女突然暈底，而你又識急救，呢個時候你又可以名正言順咁將隻手放係佢個胸上面，又可以人工呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n如果你公司冇女就算啦</blockquote><br />\n擺得都死左"},{"pid":"dbd2478f5ba94646105dce35139d45f3deb38624","tid":220462,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>份工有需要咪去考 如果唔係考完真係無乜機會用番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩工會有用<br />\n做開文職工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇乜機會用<br />\n<br />\n除非你公司有條好撚索既女突然暈底，而你又識急救，呢個時候你又可以名正言順咁將隻手放係佢個胸上面，又可以人工呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n如果你公司冇女就算啦</blockquote><br />\n擺得都死左</blockquote><br />\n咁又唔一定係for返工用嘅....除非你人生得返工<br />\n你玩戶外活動, 識急救是基本野吧<br />\n堂堂一個男人, 出事個陣淨係識企係到叫救命唔通又好型咩<br />\n<br />\n雖然考完有99%時間係冇用, 但做人嘅野唔知幾時出意外, 你有興趣又有時間咪考來看門口"},{"pid":"1397ac6ddd4bfad8c8a4fe09a23bf2f11dcb9e95","tid":220462,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c176f9cd0d4bdcf8ec4c36944a25a753b53a9c30","tid":220462,"uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:50:37.000Z","msg":"睇吓你做邊行"},{"pid":"6716f9b7e2c8c567a7a7713c39cbe6713186d12c","tid":220462,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:04:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbcb64f1e1eb2e3f5b5951590289fd929c242e16","tid":220462,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:06:47.000Z","msg":"冇用。<br />\n9成9人學完, 見到有人出事都唔會施救<br />\n香港都冇好撒瑪利亞人法"},{"pid":"92bf6a07061843be9d856df972596ef5bd718c84","tid":220462,"uid":15817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要RENEW 架喎<br />\n你有冇咁多effort 去保住個資格</blockquote><br />\n都係每3年renew一次啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9371696cc46a7f0cf350f1f41c520143f90e2171","tid":220462,"uid":102029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"自我增值嘅技能黎架姐 <br />\n想學咪學"},{"pid":"118467474aeba31d0cb9b0efd3b4d13b9329dfe9","tid":220462,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇吓你做邊行</blockquote><br />\n保安同物管一定要<br />\n每個 office 和 facility 皆設 First-aid Box<br />\n而每個First-aid Box一定會貼上兩個掃帚的姓名同手提號碼</blockquote><br />\nD 中小企9成都唔識呢d<br />\n查起上來9成中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f796b6fa1145d11b0770704f836bafb99a50326","tid":220462,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"學左可唔可以當進修費用, 報稅個陣寫埋<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔想益正苦"},{"pid":"f2ddbb4210665139e0d2cf5a31f4f601b91cae7d","tid":220462,"uid":64336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"康文署有啲職位要有firs